To Compile:

1 - Run this command in the Dynamic Style Sheets directory:
		apxs -c -i -a mod_dss.c
	* Note: When I ran apxs it installed the module in the wrong folder so I added
	* a symbolic link in the correct folder
		
2 - In your Apache Configuration add:	
		LoadModule dss_module modules/mod_dss.so
		
3 - In your Virtual Host file add:	
		AddHandler dss-handler .dss
	